id: lbm_board_config
label: LoRa Basic Modem Board Configuration
package: lorawan_extension
description: >
  This component implements LoRa Basic Modem Hardware Abstraction Layer for Series 2 devices with Semtech transceiver.
  It provides board-specific configuration options for the LoRa Basic Modem.
category: LBM HAL
quality: experimental
ui_hints:
  visibility: never
provides:
  - name: lbm_board_config

requires:
  - name: lbm_brd4400c_config
    condition: [brd4400c]
